00:00:20.780 --> 00:00:23.500
Okay. why the competition between you ?

00:00:24.020 --> 00:00:26.920
Needle is an important thing in life..

00:00:27.460 --> 00:00:29.180
It brings together what's been separated..

00:00:29.180 --> 00:00:32.820
So, you all go together and buy it..

00:00:33.600 --> 00:00:35.140
All right. Come on everyone..

00:00:37.020 --> 00:00:38.680
Shopkeeper.. Give us a needle..

00:00:38.900 --> 00:00:39.620
