00:01:07.260 --> 00:01:10.420
Give us a needle big enough for the five of us to carry together..

00:01:11.100 --> 00:01:15.240
Mmm.. looks like they don't have anything inside their skull..

00:01:15.860 --> 00:01:18.860
I'll sell them the useless cut out palm tree..

00:01:19.380 --> 00:01:24.300
Oh.. You're asking for a big needle.. Why didn't you say that earlier..

00:01:24.600 --> 00:01:28.940
Give me 20 rupees and take the big needle that's out there..

00:01:29.680 --> 00:01:31.760
Did you guys see that.. Did you ?

00:01:32.120 --> 00:01:36.520
You can't buy good stuff if you're not smart enough.. Lift up the needle..

00:01:45.700 --> 00:01:49.460
What is this.. what are you guys carrying..?

00:01:49.680 --> 00:01:52.640
It's a needle that we bought for our Guru..

00:01:55.900 --> 00:01:59.860
A needle ? I've never seen a needle like this..

00:01:59.860 --> 00:02:04.680
Mhumm.. Known is a drop, unknown is an ocean..

00:02:05.020 --> 00:02:07.620
Come take lessons from our Guru..

00:02:07.620 --> 00:02:09.620
And then you'll know about this..

00:02:15.520 --> 00:02:20.940
Huh?! They're carrying a palm tree?
What is this ?

00:02:21.100 --> 00:02:23.980
Needle to sew your clothes, Guru..

00:02:24.480 --> 00:02:28.560
Perhaps a needle this big has been launched now..

00:02:29.460 --> 00:02:33.320
Never show what we do not know to people..

00:02:33.560 --> 00:02:35.900
Only then I could be a great man..

00:02:35.900 --> 00:02:39.180
That's what my Guru said.. I'll follow that..

00:02:39.560 --> 00:02:41.120
What's your doubt, Guru

00:02:41.520 --> 00:02:43.500
